<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77d8ec3d-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s74"><num value="74">§ 74.</num><heading> Rules and regulations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary of the Treasury shall make such rules and regulations as are necessary for the carrying out of the provisions of <ref href="/us/usc/t15/s73">section 73 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77d8ec3e-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">(<ref href="/us/act/1916-09-08/ch463">Sept. 8, 1916, ch. 463</ref>, title VIII, § 803, <ref href="/us/stat/39/799">39 Stat. 799</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
